51
00:03:44,441 --> 00:03:45,841
The preparatory exercises just now

52
00:03:46,202 --> 00:03:48,522
were meant to help me

53
00:03:48,881 --> 00:03:51,441
establish a harmonious energy field
with you.

54
00:03:51,762 --> 00:03:54,042
This special energy of mine

55
00:03:55,082 --> 00:03:58,042
is here to bring you benefits.

56
00:03:58,841 --> 00:03:59,922
What benefits, you ask?

57
00:04:00,362 --> 00:04:03,681
In life, there are essentially
two things:

58
00:04:04,482 --> 00:04:08,121
money and health.

59
00:04:19,281 --> 00:04:19,781
Money.

60
00:04:28,161 --> 00:04:31,442
The spring breeze of reform
swept through Yuehai.

61
00:04:33,522 --> 00:04:35,962
The night school grandly opened,
welcoming spring.

62
00:04:41,361 --> 00:04:45,082
According to Meng Xiaoli's
incomplete count,

63
00:04:45,161 --> 00:04:47,864
