75
00:05:21,601 --> 00:05:23,642
Everyone's eyes lit up
like they were seeing gold.

76
00:05:23,801 --> 00:05:24,562
They were gleaming.

77
00:05:24,841 --> 00:05:26,801
The town government compound
looked resplendent.

78
00:05:27,041 --> 00:05:30,082
Factory owners and ordinary folks

79
00:05:30,322 --> 00:05:32,041
sat together as family,
listening closely.

80
00:05:32,442 --> 00:05:34,002
They discussed how to make money

81
00:05:34,841 --> 00:05:36,122
and how to prosper together.

82
00:05:36,281 --> 00:05:38,082
They praised
how well the night school ran.

83
00:05:38,202 --> 00:05:39,401
Knowledge is power.

84
00:05:39,601 --> 00:05:40,442
Using all strokes,

85
00:05:40,522 --> 00:05:41,921
our residents swam freely in...

86
00:05:41,962 --> 00:05:44,241
Sir, lower your voice.
We can hear you in the hallway.

87
00:05:46,562 --> 00:05:49,202
They swam freely in our Yuehai.

88
00:05:51,442 --> 00:05:52,041
Mr. Xie,

89
00:05:52,401 --> 00:05:54,360
I didn't expect you
to be so good at organizing.

90
00:05:54,721 --> 00:05:56,024
The first night school session

91
00:05:56,202 --> 00:05:58,642
was organized so quickly.

92
00:05:59,322 --> 00:06:00,442
And the results are so good.

93
00:06:00,762 --> 00:06:03,601
It is thanks to your excellent idea.

94
00:06:03,801 --> 00:06:04,841
Mr. Zheng said himself.

95
00:06:05,481 --> 00:06:07,122
"Ms. Li's idea was excellent.

96
00:06:07,642 --> 00:06:08,801
It keeps pace with the times,

97
00:06:09,202 --> 00:06:11,841
lifting our Yuehai to a new level.

98
00:06:12,041 --> 00:06:13,481
But we mustn't be satisfied.

99
00:06:13,762 --> 00:06:16,401
We must make it bigger, stronger,
and achieve real success."

100
00:06:17,962 --> 00:06:19,281
