105
00:06:31,082 --> 00:06:34,281
We need to advance gradually,
staying grounded.

106
00:06:39,002 --> 00:06:40,082
- Alright?
- I think so too.

107
00:06:45,442 --> 00:06:46,601
I had no clue yesterday.

108
00:06:46,682 --> 00:06:47,601
- Yes.
- Got something today.

109
00:06:47,736 --> 00:06:49,361
Class is starting. Where are you going?

110
00:06:49,361 --> 00:06:51,082
Yes. I need to make a call.
Be right there.

111
00:06:51,122 --> 00:06:51,762
You go ahead.

112
00:06:51,762 --> 00:06:52,322
Zheng.

113
00:07:02,098 --> 00:07:06,481
(Welcome to use the public phone.
Coin slot)

114
00:07:06,481 --> 00:07:07,122
Zheng.

115
00:07:07,522 --> 00:07:08,082
Got class?

116
00:07:08,281 --> 00:07:08,781
Yes.

117
00:07:09,810 --> 00:07:12,095
(City Construction Archives)

118
00:07:25,082 --> 00:07:25,582
Hello?

119
00:07:26,721 --> 00:07:28,522
Mr. Zheng, I knew it was you.

120
00:07:29,522 --> 00:07:31,281
I've been waiting.
What took you so long?

121
00:07:31,762 --> 00:07:32,762
Stop talking.

122
00:07:32,762 --> 00:07:34,601
Listen to me.
I'm in a hurry to get to class.

123
00:07:35,522 --> 00:07:36,882
About the night school teachers,

124
00:07:37,082 --> 00:07:38,601
you must vet them carefully.

125
00:07:39,182 --> 00:07:42,202
Here's the thing. At the place
where I'm having class right now,

126
00:07:42,481 --> 00:07:43,962
my classmate come from everywhere.

127
00:07:44,642 --> 00:07:47,202
They told me
that many people across the country

128
00:07:47,442 --> 00:07:49,304
are taking advantage
of 'knowledge explosion'

129
00:07:49,562 --> 00:07:51,992
to pose as masters and experts
and deceive people everywhere.

130
00:07:52,361 --> 00:07:54,801
So we must be extra cautious
when selecting teachers.

131
00:07:55,122 --> 00:07:55,801
Do you hear me?

132
00:07:56,682 --> 00:07:57,882
We are on the same page.

133
00:07:58,481 --> 00:07:59,882
Well,

134
00:08:00,182 --> 00:08:01,481
I just went to see Ms. Li.

135
00:08:01,702 --> 00:08:02,962
I was about to tell you this.

136
00:08:03,322 --> 00:08:05,801
I did the screening,
and Ms. Li double-checked.

137
00:08:06,041 --> 00:08:07,082
The person we chose

138
00:08:07,122 --> 00:08:09,522
is the top expert in the nation.

139
00:08:10,002 --> 00:08:11,281
He'll boost our night school.

140
00:08:11,562 --> 00:08:13,921
Don't worry. Everything is excellent.

141
00:08:14,522 --> 00:08:16,382
So let's get back to work, okay?

142
00:08:16,682 --> 00:08:17,442
I need to go.

143
00:08:18,122 --> 00:08:20,041
Mr. Tan has no problem with it at all.

144
00:08:20,522 --> 00:08:22,322
Okay, that's settled. Bye.

145
00:08:22,801 --> 00:08:23,642
Alright.

146
00:08:30,401 --> 00:08:32,001
Xie. Xie. Xie.

147
00:08:32,082 --> 00:08:33,202
- I...
- Wait a second.

148
00:08:33,202 --> 00:08:33,841
I need to eat.

149
00:08:34,442 --> 00:08:36,162
I have a lot to do.
I haven't eaten today.

150
00:08:36,162 --> 00:08:38,402
I want to discuss a problem with you.

151
00:08:39,202 --> 00:08:40,241
Okay, let's talk there.

152
00:08:40,361 --> 00:08:40,861
No, no.

153
00:08:40,881 --> 00:08:42,121
We can talk while I eat.

154
00:08:42,402 --> 00:08:43,042
Xie.

155
00:08:44,322 --> 00:08:46,282
We shouldn't discuss this
in front of everyone.

156
00:08:46,402 --> 00:08:49,001
I have some issues to discuss with you.

157
00:08:49,442 --> 00:08:49,962
What's wrong?

158
00:08:50,761 --> 00:08:52,282
Take a look at this first.

159
00:08:55,202 --> 00:09:00,001
On the ten key issues about Xie Chunlai
acting as the mayor of Yuehai.

160
00:09:01,521 --> 00:09:02,202
You wrote this?

161
00:09:02,601 --> 00:09:03,101
Yes, I did.

162
00:09:04,442 --> 00:09:05,162
You're full?

163
00:09:06,202 --> 00:09:07,001
Then get a life.

164
00:09:08,082 --> 00:09:09,521
Xie, you...

165
00:09:10,282 --> 00:09:11,481
Don't get emotional, okay?

166
00:09:11,481 --> 00:09:12,402
I'm not emotional.

167
00:09:12,402 --> 00:09:13,282
I don't have time.

168
00:09:13,282 --> 00:09:14,121
- Wait.
- I don't have time.

169
00:09:14,121 --> 00:09:14,641
Take a look.

170
00:09:14,841 --> 00:09:17,001
My report is based on facts.

171
00:09:17,042 --> 00:09:19,521
I put it down on paper
only after careful consideration.

172
00:09:19,601 --> 00:09:20,361
You're jealous?

173
00:09:20,962 --> 00:09:21,761
