184
00:09:35,601 --> 00:09:37,562
Now I see
that I was absolutely right to do so.

185
00:09:37,601 --> 00:09:38,402
You're running away.

186
00:09:39,162 --> 00:09:41,442
Now recall carefully.
Let me help you recall.

187
00:09:41,682 --> 00:09:43,521
When you proposed
launching this night school,

188
00:09:43,562 --> 00:09:44,442
