214
00:10:24,402 --> 00:10:24,902
No.

215
00:10:25,202 --> 00:10:25,721
What? Why?

216
00:10:25,802 --> 00:10:27,082
We see an issue, we fix it.

217
00:10:27,481 --> 00:10:29,121
- We must seek truth from facts.
- Okay?

218
00:10:29,802 --> 00:10:31,361
I want you to read this carefully.

219
00:10:31,402 --> 00:10:31,902
We...

220
00:10:33,042 --> 00:10:33,542
Yes.

221
00:10:34,282 --> 00:10:36,001
- What?
- When I've calmed down,

222
00:10:36,282 --> 00:10:37,841
I will definitely read through

223
00:10:38,001 --> 00:10:39,962
the problem report
you wrote specifically for me.

224
00:10:40,962 --> 00:10:42,001
But I'm not calm now.

225
00:10:42,241 --> 00:10:43,761
Alright, so when will you be calm?

226
00:10:44,922 --> 00:10:46,481
Is there ever a calm moment in Yuehai?

227
00:10:46,601 --> 00:10:47,322
I'm starving.

228
00:10:47,481 --> 00:10:48,202
What do you mean?

229
00:10:50,001 --> 00:10:53,241
I mean 'striving.' For perfection.
It's my work attitude.

230
00:10:55,682 --> 00:10:56,182
Fine.

231
00:10:56,442 --> 00:10:57,361
Xie Chunlai, listen.

232
00:10:57,442 --> 00:10:58,721
While you're eating,

233
00:10:58,802 --> 00:10:59,761
calm yourself down.

234
00:11:00,442 --> 00:11:01,481
And read that report.

235
00:11:01,501 --> 00:11:02,802
There's no avoiding this.

236
00:11:10,202 --> 00:11:11,282
Professor He.

237
00:11:14,001 --> 00:11:14,682
Professor He.

238
00:11:24,121 --> 00:11:24,841
What's wrong?

239
00:11:25,082 --> 00:11:26,442
Are you feeling unwell?

240
00:11:26,601 --> 00:11:28,402
It's nothing. Don't worry too much.

241
00:11:28,841 --> 00:11:29,761
It's not a big problem.

242
00:11:30,121 --> 00:11:32,042
